Package org.sd.util.cmd

Interface Summary
CommandExecutor Interface for executing a specific command.
Commands Interface for commands to be executed by the command interpreter.
 

Class Summary
AbstractExecutor Abstract implementation of a command executor.
BaseCommands Base commands implementation that sets up default generic commands.
CommandInterpreter Interpreter for creating a command-line utility.
HelpExecutor A command executor for giving command help.
QuitExecutor A command executor for giving command quit.
VarsExecutor A command executor for giving command vars.
